MODE perl

ASPELL >=0.60.1

MAGIC /0:256:^[ \t]*\#!((\/\w*)+)\/perl/pl/pm
MAGIC /<noregex>/pl/pm

DESCRIPTION mode for checking Perl comments and string literals

FILTER url
FILTER context
